2000-10-05  Katsumi Yamaoka    <yamaoka@jpl.org>

	* wl-summary.el: Don't use the 3rd argument of `require' because
	it might be ignored by some wrappers (e.g. jam-zcat, efs, etc.).
	* wl-util.el: Ditto.
	* wl-draft.el: Ditto.

